title: Challenger Jungler Doing Coaching! Read post for details
body:
**Doing Jungle Coaching
I'm currently a challenger jungle main and i think i can help quite a few people with improving/climbing with jungle.  
Done 2 lessons so far and they went really well so I wouldn't mind doing it for anyone interested! **

_________________________________
**VOD Review + Op.GG = $10 
Live Game + Review/Talk about it after = $15 
(Only accepting paypal atm)**
_________________________________

Lessons should be around an Hour long. 
Anything else or extra stuff can be negotiated!

Add me on league or join my discord channel, you can ask me general questions about the game/coaching/w.e
